    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>成为人类最后的希望，组织村民对抗没日没夜出兵进犯的魔王军!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882040/extras/06ebb6805810af02098901c5f8c27d96.poster.avif?t=1727408478\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882040/extras/06ebb6805810af02098901c5f8c27d96.webm?t=1727408478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882040/extras/06ebb6805810af02098901c5f8c27d96.mp4?t=1727408478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >采集资源，设计、建造并升级基地和生产资源；研究武器，布置陷阱和塔防，招募佣兵并出发到随机生成且不停变化的地下城中，击败一个又一个大魔王！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882040/extras/14b900fbe414de8c647812bc79b8b7cd.avif?t=1727408478\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在野外挖掘各种资源，冶炼金属、种植树木、养殖牛羊来喂饱嗷嗷待哺的村民们<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882040/extras/169603127524365ca807e82da5b38a88.poster.avif?t=1727408478\" width=600 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882040/extras/169603127524365ca807e82da5b38a88.webm?t=1727408478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882040/extras/169603127524365ca807e82da5b38a88.mp4?t=1727408478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >研究科技解锁武器制造、魔法、电力乃至自动化生产和防御，逐步实现勇者的躺赢大业<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882040/extras/1b54bdb95e0df57deb54a68185108039.poster.avif?t=1727408478\" width=600 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882040/extras/1b54bdb95e0df57deb54a68185108039.webm?t=1727408478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882040/extras/1b54bdb95e0df57deb54a68185108039.mp4?t=1727408478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >规划基地布局，巧妙安排围墙、箭塔、陷阱的搭配并升级，坑杀一波波怪物大军<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882040/extras/b828f9c39187d34cb174a2db906ca46c.poster.avif?t=1727408478\" width=600 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882040/extras/b828f9c39187d34cb174a2db906ca46c.webm?t=1727408478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882040/extras/b828f9c39187d34cb174a2db906ca46c.mp4?t=1727408478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >招兵买马探索每天动态变化的地城，搜刮战利品，累积击杀分数并解锁成就<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882040/extras/337f24468796133973fe75a61f3e5a1f.poster.avif?t=1727408478\" width=600 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882040/extras/337f24468796133973fe75a61f3e5a1f.webm?t=1727408478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882040/extras/337f24468796133973fe75a61f3e5a1f.mp4?t=1727408478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败守门魔王，进入沙漠、熔岩和冰原等新生态，面对新的挑战并改造基地适应新环境<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882040/extras/a2b2d99c8e8c5f0f3a1949dcb8f1edf0.poster.avif?t=1727408478\" width=600 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882040/extras/a2b2d99c8e8c5f0f3a1949dcb8f1edf0.webm?t=1727408478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882040/extras/a2b2d99c8e8c5f0f3a1949dcb8f1edf0.mp4?t=1727408478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >轻松切换战法弓三大职业、正副手武器随心搭配，招兵买马、直捣魔窟</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882040/extras/e35350c856f6bb04954ccfdba87ceb15.poster.avif?t=1727408478\" width=616 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882040/extras/e35350c856f6bb04954ccfdba87ceb15.webm?t=1727408478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882040/extras/e35350c856f6bb04954ccfdba87ceb15.mp4?t=1727408478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
